<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 21:10:56 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>三星推出配备高通芯片和增强人工智能功能的 Galaxy S25 手机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-unveils-galaxy-s25-phone-with-qualcomm-chips-enhanced-ai-features-2025-01-22/</link><description>三星电子周三推出了其最新的旗舰智能手机，该智能手机由高通芯片和谷歌人工智能模型提供支持，希望其升级的人工智能功能能够重振销售并抵御苹果和中国竞争对手。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 19:38:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/samsung-unveils-galaxy-s25-phone-with-qualcomm-chips-enhanced-ai-features-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普推动用关税来支付减税费用遭到国会反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-push-use-tariffs-pay-tax-cuts-faces-opposition-congress-2025-01-22/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普正在推动一项计划，明确使用提高进口商品关税的收入来帮助支付数万亿美元的减税计划，这一前所未有的转变可能会遭到国会许多共和党同僚的反对。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 19:01:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-push-use-tariffs-pay-tax-cuts-faces-opposition-congress-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>据英国《金融时报》报道，装载导弹推进剂的船只将从中国驶往伊朗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ships-loaded-with-missile-propellant-sail-china-iran-ft-reports-2025-01-22/</link><description>英国《金融时报》周三援引两个西方国家安全官员的情报报道称，两艘载有导弹推进剂原料的伊朗货船将在未来几周内从中国驶往伊朗。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 15:23:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ships-loaded-with-missile-propellant-sail-china-iran-ft-reports-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>据 CNBC 报道，高盛首席执行官表示改善中美关系非常重要</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/goldman-sachs-ceo-says-important-us-china-improve-ties-cnbc-reports-2025-01-22/</link><description>高盛首席执行官大卫·所罗门周三表示，美国和中国这两个世界上最大的经济超级大国改善双边关系非常重要。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 15:10:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/goldman-sachs-ceo-says-important-us-china-improve-ties-cnbc-reports-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着电动汽车竞争加剧，塔塔汽车希望在本地电池领域发挥作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tata-motors-looks-local-battery-play-ev-competition-rises-2025-01-22/</link><description>印度最大的电动汽车制造商塔塔汽车集团首席财务官在接受采访时表示，该公司认为，本地制造的电动汽车电池将有助于其在新产品推出而竞争加剧的行业中保持优势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 13:20:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tata-motors-looks-local-battery-play-ev-competition-rises-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>独家：欧盟消息人士称，欧盟选择普华永道财团作为矿产、能源平台</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-picks-pwc-consortium-minerals-energy-platform-eu-source-says-2025-01-22/</link><description>据欧盟委员会消息人士和路透社看到的文件称，欧盟已选择普华永道和斯洛伐克软件公司开发一个价值 900 万欧元（合 940 万美元）的关键矿产和能源联合采购平台。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 12:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/eu-picks-pwc-consortium-minerals-energy-platform-eu-source-says-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国公民在阿富汗北部被“杀害”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-citizen-murdered-northern-afghanistan-2025-01-22/</link><description>塔利班省警方周三表示，一名中国公民在阿富汗北部塔哈尔省被“谋杀”，并补充说已启动初步调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 12:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-citizen-murdered-northern-afghanistan-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>雅培（Abbott）依靠血糖监测仪和新产品来应对中国和汇率冲击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/abbott-forecasts-line-annual-profit-medical-device-sales-2025-01-22/</link><description>雅培公司 (Abbott Laboratories) 周三预测 2025 年利润与华尔街预期一致，因为该公司预计新设备的推出以及对其血糖监测仪不断增长的需求将抵消中国疲软和美元走强带来的打击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 12:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/abbott-forecasts-line-annual-profit-medical-device-sales-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>巴西称五家公司向中国出口大豆因污染而暂停</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazilian-soy-shipments-china-5-firms-suspended-phytosanitary-grounds-sources-2025-01-22/</link><description>巴西政府发表的一份声明证实了路透社周三从两个消息来源了解到的消息，中国是全球最大的大豆买家，由于货物不符合植物检疫要求，中国已停止接收来自五家公司的巴西大豆货物。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:21:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/brazilian-soy-shipments-china-5-firms-suspended-phytosanitary-grounds-sources-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：关税潜伏之际，特朗普转向人工智能，Netflix 飙升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-22/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:03:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>国际原子能机构负责人表示，伊朗正在为铀浓缩“踩油门”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-has-about-200-kg-uranium-enriched-near-bomb-grade-grossi-says-2025-01-22/</link><description>联合国核监督机构负责人拉斐尔·格罗西周三表示，伊朗正在“踩油门”将铀浓缩至接近武器级别，并补充说伊朗最近宣布的加速浓缩计划已开始生效。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:01:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/iran-has-about-200-kg-uranium-enriched-near-bomb-grade-grossi-says-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok 母公司字节跳动和 DeepSeek 引领中国人工智能推理领域的发展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tiktok-owner-bytedance-deepseek-lead-chinese-push-ai-reasoning-2025-01-22/</link><description>随着创建能够解决复杂问题的人工智能模型的全球竞赛愈演愈烈，TikTok 所有者字节跳动周三发布了其旗舰人工智能模型的更新。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 11:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/tiktok-owner-bytedance-deepseek-lead-chinese-push-ai-reasoning-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国允许境外机构在自贸区开展新型金融服务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-allow-foreign-intuitions-offer-new-types-financial-services-free-trade-2025-01-22/</link><description>央行周三表示，中国将在一些自贸区提供国内尚无的新型金融服务方面给予外资金融机构与国内金融机构同等的待遇。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:44:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-allow-foreign-intuitions-offer-new-types-financial-services-free-trade-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国出台鼓励保险资金入市方案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-unveils-plan-encourage-insurance-funds-into-stock-markets-2025-01-22/</link><description>中国周三表示，将引导大型国有保险公司和商业保险基金增加对A股市场的投资，这是提振落后股市的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 10:24:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-unveils-plan-encourage-insurance-funds-into-stock-markets-2025-01-22/</guid></item><item><title>印度转向地理标记来保护克什米尔标志性的“Chinar”树</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-turns-geo-tagging-conserve-kashmirs-iconic-chinar-trees-2025-01-22/</link><description>印度克什米尔当局正在对数千棵“Chinar”树进行地理标记，以创建一个全面的数据库来管理它们，并帮助在不断发展的城市化、道路拓宽项目和疾病的威胁下保护它们。</description><pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 08:50:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-turns-geo-tagging-conserve-kashmirs-iconic-chinar-trees-2025-01-22/</guid></item></channel></rss>